# ----- Math span containment -----

Unclosed math $`oops does not leak.
#               ^^^^ -markup.other.math.inline.carve
#                             ^^^^ -markup.other.math.content.carve

This paragraph after it stays ordinary prose.
#    ^^^^^^^^^ -markup.other.math.inline.carve
#                             ^^^^^^^^ -markup.other.math.content.carve

Unclosed display $$`oops also does not leak.
#                   ^^^^ -markup.other.math.display.carve

Another following paragraph stays prose.
#       ^^^^^^^^^ -markup.other.math.display.carve

Closed inline $`a+b` still works.
#             ^ punctuation.definition.math.carve
#              ^ punctuation.definition.raw.carve
#               ^^^ markup.other.math.content.carve

Closed display $$`x^2` still works.
#              ^^ punctuation.definition.math.carve
#                 ^^^ markup.other.math.content.carve

Wide math $``a ` b`` keeps its backtick.
#         ^ punctuation.definition.math.carve
#          ^^ punctuation.definition.raw.carve
#            ^^^^^ markup.other.math.content.carve
